       <div class="conText"> 
        <h1>赌球之祸，治安之虞</h1> 
        <div class="summary"> 
         <strong>时间：2013-12-29 15:04:14&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;来源：<a href="http://www.ddwhgylm.com" target="_blank"><font color="990000">道德文化公益网</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;浏览次数：<script src="http://www.ddwhgylm.com/e/public/ViewClick/?classid=35&amp;id=4622&amp;addclick=1"></script>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="#comment"><font color="990000">我来说两句(<script src="http://www.ddwhgylm.com/e/public/ViewClick/?classid=35&amp;id=4622&amp;down=2"></script>)</font></a></strong> 
         <em class="fontSize"><strong>字号：</strong><span id="font14" class="cur" onclick="javascript:doZoom(14)">T</span><b id="font16" onclick="javascript:doZoom(16)">T</b></em> 
        </div> 
        <div class="text" id="text"> 
         <p></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 26.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto" class="MsoNormal" align="center"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: '&#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial'">赌球之祸，治安之虞</span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 26.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto" class="MsoNormal" align="center"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: '&#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial'"></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">叮当</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">
           <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /-->
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">激情世界杯，四年一轮回。亿万球迷翘首期盼的南非世界杯大幕甫一拉开，各路豪强的绿荫激战便轮番上演。场上，球员们在为一个月后登上世界之巅的梦想而倾尽全力；场下，球迷们都在为各自支持的球队呐喊助威，中国球迷自然也不例外。然而，在尽享足球饕餮盛宴之余，却并非可以完全高枕无忧。与世界杯相伴而生的各种隐忧，若不慎重对待，可随时酿成严重的社会问题，甚至化“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">杯”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">成“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">悲”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">也绝非杞人忧天。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">赌球之祸</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">当前，国际上几乎所有知名赌博集团均开设有面向中国的中文赌博网站，有的直接派人入境发展下线代理，有的招揽境内赌博团伙参与投资分成。特别是随着世界杯比赛的开赛，境外赌博集团还会千万百计地将“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">网络赌球”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">渗透到境内，一些不法分子受利益驱使还会充当代理铤而走险。对此，各地警方纷纷开展专项行动，严禁网络赌球行为。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">以经济较为发达、“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">网络赌博”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">遍及至全省的浙江省为例，该省已破获的案件中所涉及的赌博网站均开办在境外，绝大多数属从境外赌博集团购买授信代理资格后，在境内发展下线，参与开设网络赌场；也有通过入股直接在境外开办赌博网站。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">“境外的一些赌博集团往往选择以内地边境地区为跳板，频频向境内渗透。”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">浙江省公安厅党委委员、副厅长董晓伟如是说，浙江已破的案件赌博团伙在境内的最上家有</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">60%</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">均指向港澳台地区及东南亚一些国家。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">当前，治理网络赌博活动面临的形势仍然非常严峻。公安机关在加大侦查力度，严惩网络赌博犯罪分子的同时，将强化对可能成为网络赌博活动利益链的第三方支付平台和网络服务商、网站租赁服务商以及网络广告宣传推广商的监管，积极构建整治网络赌博的长效工作机制。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">在北京，警方现已将利用世界杯比赛进行赌博的行为列为打击黄赌毒专项行动的重点之一。警方表示，将采用多警种协同作战等超常规手段，加大对网络赌球等网络赌博违法犯罪活动的打击力度。在过去两个月的专项行动中，一举摧毁聚众赌博团伙</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">90</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">个，其中网络赌球、网络六合彩、网络百家乐等网络赌博团伙</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">16</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">个，刑事拘留设赌抽头人员</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">189</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">人。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">同时，警方将采取加大网络巡控力度，网安、治安、刑侦等多警种联动等措施，主动发现网络赌球线索，并及时查办此类案件。同时，北京警方还将积极协调电信、银行等部门，采取封堵违法网站、冻结可疑资金账号等措施，切断违法活动的“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">资金流”、“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">信息流”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">在云南，昆明市警方将在南非世界杯期间开展集中整治网络赌博违法犯罪专项行动，提倡广大球迷健康看球。昆明市公安局官员表示，随着南非世界杯的火热开幕，网络上的赌球活动也会随之进入活跃期，因此在这期间，昆明警方将加大整治力度，严禁网络赌球行为。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">治安之虞</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">四年一度的世界杯已拉开帷幕，球迷迎来历时一个月的节日，喝酒看球成为必不可少的节日狂欢程序。据以往经验分析，世界杯期间，酒后驾车、疲劳驾驶、超速行驶等违法行为可能有所上升。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">对此，北京交管部门表示，世界杯期间，凡酒驾者，一律依法高限处罚，对醉酒驾车司机一律依法拘留，并纳入黑名单。“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">高限处罚”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">意味着司机一旦醉酒驾车，就将被拘留</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">15</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">天。在世界杯开始之前，交管部门已细致摸排了酒吧等餐饮娱乐场所分布，进行了有针对性的警力部署。交管部门将充分发挥执法小分队灵活机动的优势作用，重点围绕酒吧等餐饮娱乐场所，以及远郊旅游景点、度假村、农家乐等周边道路，加大警力投入，形成威慑高压态势，同时，在坚持全天候严查严管的基础上，将突出对</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">19</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">时至次日凌晨，以及周末、节假日酒后驾车违法高发时段的管控。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">深圳交警近日发布消息称，世界杯期间，在加强对司机宣传教育的同时，还将加大对酒后驾车违法行为的查处力度。从开幕当天起，每天晚上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">20</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">时至次日</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">7</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">时</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">30</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">分，交警将在全市布点</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">100</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">个，出动警力近千人，进行不间断的酒测行动。“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">我们不会放过任何一个心存侥幸的人，特别让民警驻守在酒楼、酒吧、休闲娱乐场所，而且查车的时间就在比赛直播前后”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">，交警局负责人表示，希望深圳球迷严格自律，酒后勿驾车，以免乐极生悲。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">世界杯期间，杭州交警将在原有基础上进一步增加夜查频率、扩大夜查规模，形成高压整治态势。特别是对酒吧、夜宵排档等场所集中区域及周边路段，将设置专门的“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">酒驾临检”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">点。杭州交警表示，公安交警部门已对酒驾整治进行了专门部署，对全市酒吧、餐饮等场所进行了全面排查。期间，数字勤务室电子巡逻与警力现场部署管理将结合起来，相邻交警大队、中队也将实行串联整治，严查酒后驾车等严重交通违法行为。杭州交警提醒广大球迷，要看精彩世界杯，开车切莫贪酒杯。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">此外，天津交管部门也表示，世界杯期间将会严查酒后驾车违法行为，并增加重点路段的夜查岗位广大球迷切忌喝酒看球后驾车出行。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">专家建议，广大球迷应调适好心态，尽量做到文明看球，至少不要酗酒闹事，聚众打人，即使有球队偏见，脾气也要收敛。球迷要调适心态，以平常心看待球赛的胜负，以欣赏和娱乐为目的，把胜负看得淡一些。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &#x2ce;&#x325;,Verdana,Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 16.5pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 5pt 21pt 5pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-right: 2.0gd; mso-para-margin-top: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 5.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">（责任编辑：李婉婷）</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang="EN-US">
           <o:p></o:p></span></p>
         <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">
           <o:p>
            &nbsp;
           </o:p></span></p> 
        </div> 
